{"tid":1663394,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[即時] 係人嘅就即刻轉場大埔討伐支那兇手","createTime":"2019-10-19T11:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T11:42:32.000Z","uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c06e7746043dd463ca341512b5c0da52d9d60719","tid":1663394,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:28:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻去中環碼頭搭307</span></span><br />\n<br />\n- 13 分鐘前<br />\n識人做Popo<br />\n兇手去咗大埔狗屋自殺<br />\n黑警唔想做condom就告鳩佢謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFact check 咗未？<br />\n消息來源係同一總區嘅Popo<br />\n以往咁多次冇單料係流<br />\n<br />\n但新聞未出街前繼續要跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw係自首 自隊一打膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 新富區社區主任胡耀昌：<br />\n「隧道斬人兇徒證實已自首（fact checked with PPRB），我現前往威爾斯醫院了解傷者情況。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MaxWuND/posts/2437674299824673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMaxWuND%2Fposts%2F2437674299824673&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=9e46420f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MaxWuND/posts/2437674299824673</a>"},{"pid":"018575e02c0d456646d5325d27cca30a27582bc7","tid":1663394,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「文宣升級」巴士流動大字報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662724</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wj3z6Ov.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwj3z6Ov.jpg&h=9f735918&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"84a3f38aa148702e7f8b826ed064e90f9eb9b1fe","tid":1663394,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"【輸出革命】一齊下載強國文宣圖！<br />\n1020 尖東<span style=\"color: red;\">向強國人<strong>輸出革命</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663011\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663011</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4oszVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4oszVJ.jpg&h=a9ec52d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyoz3kZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftyoz3kZ.png&h=39dec6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請入來下載更多文宣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663011\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663011</a>"},{"pid":"a12e634c8e1039add4d7285eba395df3530805d3","tid":1663394,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"9cbf05292c155d53f338eec5dc41b8d9d93ad09e","tid":1663394,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"佢已經自首咗"},{"pid":"bc27829cc26d084b4e2532625d786b655ab8e5ae","tid":1663394,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ftTFNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ftTFNX.jpg&h=44a0ed75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f8982e5629cc47d4ac639f19568a2284f04d168","tid":1663394,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xr